    <comment>New package python-anthropic. Part of the langchain/langgraph stack (dependency cone for skillspector): interdependent NEW packages + the langsmith bump that must be co-staged together — please stage with the sibling devel:languages:python SRs by pluskalm or builds go unresolvable.</comment>
