    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- Lower the typing_extensions dependency floor to &gt;= 4.13.2 (the version in openSUSE Leap 16.0) instead of &gt;= 4.14; the newest typing_extensions name used by the code is TypeIs, available since 4.10.0, and typing_extensions.Sentinel (added later) is not used. Verified by running the packaged offline test selection (211 passed) against typing_extensions 4.13.2.</comment>
